data.message: There was a crooked man and he walked a crooked mile.
He found a crooked sixpence upon a crooked stile.
data.name: sign-1|Ignorant

data.message: He bought a crooked cat, which caught a crooked mouse.
data.name: sign-2|Ignorant

data.message: And they all lived together in a little crooked house.
data.name: sign-3|Ignorant
